# <type>[optional scope]: <what this change solves for users>
#
# <body: address purpose, context, and what changed>
#
# [optional footer(s)]
# Closes #<issue>
# Refs #<issue>
# Co-authored-by: Name <email>
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Subject: lowercase, imperative mood, max 72 chars, no period
# Body: wrap at 72 chars
# Types: feat fix docs style refactor test chore ci build perf
# Scope: optional, e.g. feat(ci): ...
# Breaking: append ! to type, add BREAKING CHANGE trailer
# Atomic: one logical change per commit
